sentences: Alex Fergusson (born 16 December 1952) is a Scottish guitarist / record producer.
Fergusson played in the Nobodies, with Sandy Robertson (later a rock journalist of note), before forming the punk band Alternative TV with Mark Perry in 1977, and a few years later (in 1981)
